{"tid":1031836,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港交所DQ中國光纖取消其上市地位","createTime":"2019-02-22T02:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T11:37:00.000Z","uid":161853,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"98507f952e6d522bd6853e98274d89e1123534b4","tid":1031836,"uid":161853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:31:51.000Z","msg":"中國光纖（3777）公布，遭港交所（0388）勒令除牌，股份最後上市日期為今年2月13日，上市地位將在2月14日上午9時正起取消。<br />\n<br />\n中國光纖曾在去年11月9日向港交所申請復牌，港交所在11月29日決定取消其上市地位，在12月10日向上市（覆核）委員會上訴，最終委員會在今年1月30日維持撤銷中國光纖上市地位的決定。<br />\n<br />\n中國光纖在公告上指，公司股票仍繼續有效，但股份不再繼續上市，亦不再於港交所買賣。其後，公司將不再受上市規則規管。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾年前買咗呢隻辣殺股，我宜家可以做d咩，仲可唔可以換番做錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e8d421d84ef5697ab23c82f39cb298a7bc059f9","tid":1031836,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:15:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=24352900&amp;extra=&amp;page=11\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.discuss.com.hk%2Findex.php%3Faction%3Dthread%26tid%3D24352900%26extra%3D%26page%3D11&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD4oP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5SsngaE%3D&h=60242885\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=24352900&amp;extra=&amp;page=11</a><br />\n🙄🙄🙄"},{"pid":"13db9e7bace6091406249302c41cbde653b118a3","tid":1031836,"uid":168527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:30:00.000Z","msg":"點先可以攞翻啲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2aceaabdd4e49a52b262641ce6eec0034d75fe","tid":1031836,"uid":118455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:36:23.000Z","msg":"弓喜ching"},{"pid":"08917a2e76054e32c91095b460f6e01a14d02c63","tid":1031836,"uid":50386,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:38:59.000Z","msg":"值得留意是，若投資者持有被除牌的股票，由於股份被除牌後，其股份已不再可以在交易所買賣，《上市規則》已不再適用於該公司，個別股東只受該公司註冊地的法例，以及公司本身的組織章程文件規管。若投資者所持股票的公司仍於香港有註冊記錄，投資者則需向該公司直接查詢有關股東目前的權益或其它相關的手續及事項。"},{"pid":"18988809ac136f3987dae0b341628e6993a6531e","tid":1031836,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13db9e7bace6091406249302c41cbde653b118a3","tid":1031836,"uid":168527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:30:00.000Z","msg":"點先可以攞翻啲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:55:32.000Z","msg":"賣返比人"},{"pid":"968633c8df390a12c05ef3861ee96237ae243aa4","tid":1031836,"uid":68993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:56:27.000Z","msg":"揾人幫你接貨"},{"pid":"2f6f5adbd725bab5c52400afd1a01c2a34414989","tid":1031836,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:57:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4368de3b3ab22d0ae90515a8fb1fb411ac3596e4","tid":1031836,"uid":522,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:58:54.000Z","msg":"港交所成日批埋d垃圾中國公司黎香港呃錢"},{"pid":"cc2841ef84601028fc091bd227947fee38a803b2","tid":1031836,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T04:09:50.000Z","msg":"黑市買賣啦"},{"pid":"fc90b4912a3c608db599eca3f6a66b49f5b8088b","tid":1031836,"uid":161853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13db9e7bace6091406249302c41cbde653b118a3","tid":1031836,"uid":168527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:30:00.000Z","msg":"點先可以攞翻啲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"